OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScot who 'invented' chicken
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftikka masala dies          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Glaswegian chef credited with        
OL,6, inventing the chicken tikka masala has 
OL,7, died, aged 77.                         
OL,9,FAli Ahmed Aslam is said to have come up
OL,10,Fwith the dish in the 1970s when a      
OL,11,Fcustomer asked if there was a way of   
OL,12,Fmaking his chicken tikka less dry.     
OL,14,FHis solution was to add a creamy tomato
OL,15,Fsauce, in some versions of the story a 
OL,16,Fcan of tomato soup.                    
OL,18,FHis death was announced by his Shish   
OL,19,FMahal restaurant which closed for 48   
OL,20,Fhours as a mark of respect.            
